# evidence/ — populated as the experiment runs

Files that will appear here:

- `gen0-fitness-snapshot.json` — oracle output establishing the baseline (after first staging deploy of gen0 instrumentation)
- `gen1-fitness-snapshot.json` — oracle output ≥7 days after gen1 deploy
- `delta.md` — human-readable fitness delta analysis
- `pr-list.md` — links to the merged PRs that produced gen1
- `post-mortem.md` — adversarial review after gen1 closes (what went well, what didn't, what to change for gen2)
- `oracle-runs.jsonl` — raw oracle outputs (one per line) for any run during the experiment window
